WEBVTT

1
00:39:49.090 --> 00:39:50.380 
啊呃  呃
Uh-uh, uh-uh!

2
00:39:50.470 --> 00:39:52.090 
等一会
Just a minute.

3
00:39:53.470 --> 00:39:57.740 
