Supper's not quite ready. You'll just have time to wash.

4
00:39:58.100 --> 00:40:00.060 
洗手  洗手
Wash? Wash?

5
00:40:00.140 --> 00:40:02.260 
洗手  洗手  洗手
Wash? Wash? Wash?

6
00:40:02.260 --> 00:40:04.230 
哈  我就知道她有诡计
Hah ! Knew there was a catch to it.

7
00:40:06.230 --> 00:40:09.400 
