-Why wash? -What for? We ain't goin' nowhere.

8
00:40:09.490 --> 00:40:11.490 
过年啦
'Tain't New Year's.

9
00:40:12.280 --> 00:40:14.700 
也许你们已经洗过了
Oh, perhaps you have washed.

10
00:40:14.780 --> 00:40:16.410 
也许我们
Perhaps we...

11
00:40:16.950 --> 00:40:22.120 
-对呀  也许洗过了  -什么时候
-Yes! Perhaps we have. -But when?

